				<ul>
	<li><a href="http://indigo.uic.edu/" target="_blank"><strong>INDIGO </strong></a>(UIC&#39;s Institutional Repository)</li>
	<li><strong><a href="http://www.uic.edu/htbin/cgiwrap/bin/ojs/index.php/" target="_blank">Journals@UIC</a>&nbsp;</strong>Start your own open access journal</li>
